    "# GOES Derived Motion Winds"
   ],

   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "from goes2go.data import goes_nearesttime\n",
    "\n",
    "# Tools from https://github.com/blaylockbk/Carpenter_Workshop\n",
    "from toolbox.wind import spddir_to_uv\n",
    "from toolbox.cartopy_tools import common_features, pc\n",
    "from paint.standard2 import cm_wind"
   ],
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "source": [
    "# Download Level-2 derived motion wind ABI product\n",
    "gwnd = goes_nearesttime('2021-09-16 18:00', product='ABI-L2-DMWVC')"
   ],

    "# Download ABI Multi-channel product (for RGB background)\n",
    "g = goes_nearesttime(\"2021-09-16 18:00\", product=\"ABI\")"
   ],
   "outputs": [
    {
     "output_type": "stream",
     "name": "stdout",

     ]
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "source": [
    "# Convert GOES wind speed and direction to u- and v-wind components\n",
    "gu, gv = spddir_to_uv(gwnd.wind_speed, gwnd.wind_direction)"
   ],
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "source": [
    "# Plot winds on a PlateCarree map\n",
    "ax = common_features(\"10m\", dark=True, figsize=[15, 10], STATES=True)\n",
    "ax.barbs(\n",
    "    gwnd.lon,\n",
    "    gwnd.lat,\n",
    "    gu,\n",
    "    gv,\n",
    "    gwnd.wind_speed,\n",
    "    **cm_wind().cmap_kwargs,\n",
    "    length=5,\n",
    ")\n"
   ],
   "outputs": [
    {
     "output_type": "execute_result",
     "data": {

   "source": [
    "# Plot winds on a Geostationary map\n",
    "ax = common_features(\"10m\", dark=True, figsize=[15, 10], STATES=True, crs=g.FOV.crs)\n",
    "ax.barbs(\n",
    "    gwnd.lon.data,\n",

   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "# Plot on Geostationary map with NaturalColor RGB product \n",
    "\n",
    "ax = common_features(\"10m\", dark=True, figsize=[15, 10], STATES=True, crs=g.FOV.crs)\n",
    "ax.barbs(\n",
    "    gwnd.lon.data,\n",
    "    gwnd.lat.data,\n",
    "    gu.data,\n",
    "    gv.data,\n",
    "    gwnd.wind_speed,\n",
    "    **cm_wind().cmap_kwargs,\n",
    "    length=5,\n",
    "    transform=pc,\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.imshow(g.rgb.NaturalColor(), **g.FOV.imshow_kwargs)\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.set_title(f\"{g.orbital_slot} Natural Color and Derived Motion Winds\", loc='left', fontweight='bold')\n",
    "ax.set_title(f\"{g.t.dt.strftime('%H:%M UTC %d-%b-%Y').item()}\", loc=\"right\")"
